wikipedia_page.main: Jayne Barnetson (born 21 January 1968) is a Scottish former athlete who competed mainly in the High jump. She finished fourth at the 1986 World Junior Championships. Her 1989 Scottish records for the high jump (1.91m) and Heptathlon (5803 pts), still stand.
